    "description": {
      "value": "<p><em>As you produce a wild surge, you bottle the magic within yourself for later use.</em></p><p><strong>Reaction</strong> - 1/Short Rest - Magical</p><p>When you roll a Wild Surge, you can choose to delay the surge's effects. You store the surge for up to 1 hour, and can trigger the surge at any time using another reaction. If you do not trigger the surge within 1 hour, it then triggers automatically.</p>",
